description:
Non material minor amendment of planning permission ref: P110392 dated 8 February 2012 for the demolition of the existing building and structures and erection of a 6-storey building, plus basement with mezzanine level and roof top plant enclosure, providing for a total of 9,703sqm (GEA) composed of: 6,834sqm (GEA) business (use class B1) and 2,869sqm (GEA) of flexible shop/restaurant/caf√©/drinking establishment floor space (use classes A1/A3/A4) together with associated works. The amendments are: 
- repositioning of photo voltaic panels, plant enclosures and biodiverse roof;
- alterations to doors, fenestration and shopfront detail at ground floor level; 
- alterations to a door on the front elevation on the northern elevation;
- repositioning of doors and louvres on the southern elevation; 
- removal of textured brick feature on the southern elevation; and
- changes to basement and mezzanine level layouts.
